<D>__{yankee poodle.}
<C>__{groucho}
<D>__{i've got just the place for a man like you but i'm too busy right now to do any digging. what do you call your dog when you want him?}
<C>__{chico}
<D>__{i don't want him.}
<C>__{groucho}
<D>__{well, if you don't want your dog why don't you put him in a pound?}
